          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to aggregate and present customer charge data for reporting purposes. It consolidates various financial metrics related to customer billing into a single, summarized view. The view calculates the total amount due by summing several financial components from the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Nypa.UploadNYPACoverSheet",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table, specifically for records identified by the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "CoverSheetRecordType",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " of '20'. It also extracts net energy and demand metrics for further analysis."
        }
