          "text": "This view is used in financial reporting and analysis contexts where a summary of customer charges is required. It provides a consolidated view of billing data, which can be used by financial analysts, accountants, or business intelligence tools to generate reports, track billing trends, and ensure accurate financial records. The specific filtering on "
